\begin_layout Section
Blue water
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Blue water, simply put, is flowing water.
 It is the liquid water in rivers and under the ground (aquifers).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The blue water footprint is the use of it by humans.
 Think drinking water, showers, irrigation,
