Focusing on water footprint can promote unnatural systems
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
When comparing the water footprint of different types of livestock farming,
 it was noticed that for cattle, industrial systems have a lower water footprint
 than systems where cows are allowed to graze freely.
\end_layout

